<h2>A New Bloodline Rises</h2>
<p>
    Will you forge a fresh path, or honor the ancestors resting within the <a href="/highscores">Hall of Champions</a>?
    Blood, gold, and glory are etched in <a href="/statistics">The Tome of Lore</a>, while the <a href="/races">Chronicles of Ancestry</a> detail the unique traits of the lineages that walk this realm.
</p>
<p>Under what name shall the first chapter of your dynasty be written, and from which ancestry do you hail?</p>

<form action="/start" method="post">
    <div class="form-row">
        <input type="text" class="form-input" name="name" maxlength="18" placeholder="Enter your name, Heir" required />
        <select class="form-select" name="select_race">
            <% races.forEach(race => { %>
                <option value="<%= race.id %>"><%= race.emoji %> <%= race.label %></option>
            <% }) %>
        </select>
        <button type="submit" class="btn">🚩 Start</button>
    </div>
</form>
